FT  31 MAY 94 / International Company News: ACP Publishing
Mr Kerry Packer's ACP Publishing has acquired a 46 per cent interest in the
Vietnam Investment Review, one of the country's English-language business
weeklies and the author of the BHP-GE story.
The VIR was launched by a group of expatriate Australians in 1991, and is
published by the Vietnamese State Committee for Co-operation and Investment,
making it a semi-official publication.
